name: Life is not happening to you. You happen to life.
description: We are at the center of the universe. Imagine that you are a happy, successful, creative person. The way you want to be. Only you are the creator of your success, happiness and happy accidents. You can prepare your way and the likelihood of success will be astronomical. Nobody knows how your dreams will come true, but know that they will come true... 01.07.2021
